I naively thought

54
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,520
I could protect you

55
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,040
but I didn't expect

56
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,280
to be the person to hurt you the most

57
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,240
and you are the one
who has been hurt the most.

58
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,680
You shouldered

59
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,640
all the pain yourself.

60
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,520
It's none of your business.

61
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,560
No matter what,

62
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,440
I also hope

63
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,560
you can cheer up.

64
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,520
Just like the capable person
you once were.

65
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,120
As your family,

66
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,520
I will always support you,

67
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,760
Sister.

68
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,320
I'm home now. Don't worry.

69
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,840
Cheng Ning is busy today.

70
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,480
She ordered me

71
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,640
to accompany you.

72
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,200
I'm not a child.

73
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,080
If you want to accompany me,

74
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,680
drink with me.

75
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,280
Wei,

76
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,160
