79
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,280
I'm different from him.

80
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,400
Wei,

81
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:20,160
I've prescribed some medicine
that helps you sleep.

82
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,520
Then,

83
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,680
you'll be able to sleep well

84
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,360
after taking the medicine.

85
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,560
When you wake up,

86
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,480
you can begin

87
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,760
a new life.

88
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,840
All right. I'll listen to Dr. Qiu

89
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,120
and begin a new life.

90
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:46,920
Go back.

91
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,480
I will rest well.

92
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:54,000
Take good care of yourself.

93
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,720
I'm leaving.

94
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,200
Take care.

95
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,200
Don't worry.

96
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:00,600
All right.

97
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,360
Remember to use the blanket.

98
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,080
How dare you harm her!

99
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:15,920
I didn't!

100
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,160
Do you think I didn't know

101
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,440
it was your idea
to call the reporters to the hotel?

102
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,240
You almost killed her

103
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,120
