104
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,080
I only wanted you to give up completely.

105
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,760
It was Yun Shasha who drugged her.

106
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,560
You should keep an eye
on your fiancee instead!

107
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,360
