108
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,880
I won't let anyone else hurt Xu Wei.

109
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,080
I will protect her.

110
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,680
Who are you to protect her?

111
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,200
Her younger brother?

112
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,320
She also sees you

113
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,960
as her younger brother.

114
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,160
But I can love her.

115
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,400
Can you?

116
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,360
Even if I'm her younger brother,

117
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,440
I will also protect her forever.

118
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,640
Yu, you...

119
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,480
I knew all about the filthy things

120
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:55,800
