121
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:58,600
Don't listen to Qiu Yu.
I didn't do anything.

122
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,480
I will

123
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,960
forget about this

124
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,720
for Madam Yun's sake.

125
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,080
In the future,

126
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,240
if I see you hurting Xu Wei
with these methods,

127
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,680
I won't forgive you.

128
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,080
Yu,

129
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:13,040
I did everything for you.

130
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,640
Please forgive me.

131
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,400
Don't call me your brother.

132
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,400
I don't see you as my younger sister.

133
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,640
I will never marry you.

134
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,040
Yu,

135
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,120
