150
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,600
It's all right.

151
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,600
Hello.

152
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,320
Qiu Yu, it's all your fault.

153
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,720
Yu and I

154
