172
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,400
Yu.

173
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,480
Yu.

174
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:45,640
I knew you wouldn't ignore me.

175
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,160
Yu.

176
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,240
Yu.

177
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,080
Yu.

178
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,120
Yu.

